Requirements: php 8.1, Composer

step.1 create .env file and configure database DB_CONNECTION=mysql, DB_PORT=3306, 
        DB_USERNAME=task, DB_USERNAME=root.
step.2 Run command [php artisan migrate] to create database tables.
step.3 Run command [php artisan serve]
step.4 In browser run http://localhost:8000 or http://127.0.0.1:8000 
step.5 Click register and make an account.
step.6 In dashboard page Click admin and then click Show News Table 
       to call api get data stored in the database and show in the datatable.